MAIL: Send and receive in-game mail

Syntax: mail read
        mail send <player>
        mail list
        mail delete <number>

DESCRIPTION:
  The in-game mail system lets you send messages to other players
  that they will receive on their next login.

  mail read        : read your current message
  mail send <name> : compose a message to a player
  mail list        : list all messages in your mailbox
  mail delete <n>  : delete message number n

SEE ALSO: post, communication, forward

